# Aircraft Telemetry Dashboard Rules

- Use Flask app factory pattern
- Use Blueprints for every module
- Use SQLAlchemy ORM
- Use Marshmallow schemas
- Use JWT authentication
- Use UUID primary keys
- Write modular production-grade code
- Avoid monolithic files
- Add error handling everywhere
- Add logging for all APIs
- Use service-layer architecture
- Use environment variables
- Follow REST API conventions
- Use Socket.IO for realtime updates
- Use Tailwind CSS on frontend
- Use React functional components
- Use Zustand for state management
- Write scalable folder structures